A just-published report from the International Campaign for Human Rights in=
 Iran lists 217 students with sinister =91stars=92 against their names, who=
 have been barred from higher education for political activism or religious=
 belief despite performing well in entrance examinations. The Campaign beli=
eves there could be more than 1,000 =91starred=92 students =96 and that the=
re has been a =93huge jump=94 in student exclusions in the past two years.<=
BR>
