Kenya has published a list of all accredited colleges operating in the coun=
try, exposing hundreds of bogus tertiary institutions that will be closed d=
own in the second week of January. While the move signals government=92s in=
tention to clean up the higher education sector, it has caused uncertainty =
and panic among students in colleges denied accreditation.<br><a href=3D"ht=
